snippet.title: Escape from Tarkov - On The Edge of Darkness Trailer | PC Gaming Show 2024
snippet.description:
Check out the latest trailer for Escape from Tarkov. Developed by Battlestate Games, Escape From Tarkov is a realistic extraction FPS. Here's a look at what's on the way in the Escape From Tarkov 1.0 release.
